    <section>
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>I was born on September 8, 2011. My mom’s name is Alejandra and my dad’s name is Octavio. They both work and take care of a hospital. I have an older sister named Ximena. She is 18 years old.</p>
        <p>When I was little, I went skiing on the snow. I used to get mad for no reason. My first school was The Churchill School. One of my best memories is when I won my first football tournament at 6 years old. I was a sweet kid, but I was often angry.</p>
        <p>Things I liked: skiing, football, having fun. Things I disliked: getting frustrated easily. My hobbies were mostly sports and playing.</p>
